rade Request (NAS), APP Transfer, APP Maintenance, APP RPS (Help Desk)\n* APP users added to queue membership\n* Profile/permission set access to Help Desk, NAS, Raise Cash Request\n* Evaluate trading-specific permission set for role-based restrictions\n\n","url":"https://f2strategy.atlassian.net/browse/CET-119","status":"To Do","priority":"Medium","inCurrentCycle":false,"project":"Cetera","projectDescription":"","parent":{"id":"CET-110","title":"Case / TRPG Work Desk Alignment","description":""},"updatedAt":"2026-04-13T10:49:17.087-0500","assignee":{"email":"mac.nosek@f2strategy.com","name":"Mac Nosek"},"comments":[]},{"workspace":"F2","id":"CET-118","title":"Configure Lightning Page layouts","description":"**Type:** Task \n\nDynamic forms with conditional visibility per APP category:\n\n* **NAS:** Trade-specific section when Account_Setup_Type__c = Trade Request\n* **Help Desk:** Conditional sections for Transfers, Maintenance, Client Maintenance, Asset Flow Exceptions, RPS, Firm Initiatives\n\nEvaluate single dynamic page per object vs. multiple pages.","url":"https://f2strategy.atlassian.net/browse/CET-118","status":"To Do","priority":"Medium","inCurrentCycle":false,"project":"Cetera","projectDescription":"","parent":{"id":"CET-110","title":"Case / TRPG Work Desk Alignment","description":""},"updatedAt":"2026-04-13T10:49:15.790-0500","assignee":{"email":"mac.nosek@f2strategy.com","name":"Mac Nosek"},"comments":[]},{"workspace":"F2","id":"CET-116","title":"Build Help Desk automation flows ","description":"","url":"https://f2strategy.atlassian.net/browse/CET-116","status":"To Do","priority":"Medium","inCurrentCycle":false,"project":"Cetera","projectDescription":"","parent":{"id":"CET-110","title":"Case / TRPG Work Desk Alignment","description":""},"updatedAt":"2026-04-13T10:49:14.578-0500","assignee":{"email":"mac.nosek@f2strategy.com","name":"Mac Nosek"},"comments":[]},{"workspace":"F2","id":"CET-115","title":"Replicate validation rules ","description":"_Pending: